# Skill #1 - Web Hosting

Skill Demonstration Challenge

---

## Instructions

### Objective

Demonstrate web hosting using Bluehost

* Sign up for [Bluehost](http://bluehost.com) server account
* Register a custom domain at Bluehost (optional)
* Setup WordPress blog
* Create user profile page (with photo)


### Steps

* Login to the Bluehost Control panel
* Go to the Advanced tab


### Requirements

* Screen shot "bacs200/skills/xxx.png"

### Test Your Work
* Create a page for your skills "bacs200/skills/index.html"
* Include content from [Skills Index](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs200/skills/index.html)
* Go to the [Sensei Page](/unc/bacs200)
* Click on the link to the skills page
* Create this page in your skills folder


## Demonstrate Your Skill

### bluehost.png

This screen shot is proof of skill.  It shows the following ...

* Properly registered account at Bluehost
* Advanced settings of Bluehost
* Unique user ID and domain for my website
* Screen shot can be uploaded to the correct location
* Ability to create a screen shot with the correct name

